        <m:annotation encoding="application/vnd.katalysteducation.mathtex"> \prefop{\Delta}p = m \prefop{\Delta} v = \SI{6}{\kilo\gram} \cdot 10^{-3} \si{\metre\per\second} = \SI{6e-3}{\kilo\gram\metre\per\second} \text{,}</m:annotation>
